Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,流下的淚水早已乾枯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,對血感到飢渴的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡散發著\N{\fs8}\N{\r}天使柔和羽毛氣息飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗太陽不西沉的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,任誰都沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿奇術般的運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡見不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠拯救我們的神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,人們是疲憊的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,祭壇的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,機械夢想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,從黑暗甦醒的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,祭壇的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,螺絲中斷的夢想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,其乃自古命運之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,掌管死亡的兩名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗聖手誘使迷途者\N{\fs8}\N{\r}墜入業火深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,心愛的克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真高興聽到妳順利完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我誠心期待妳的歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不過﹐在那之前有項工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要請妳去做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:07.06,Title,,0,0,0,,#12 刺客行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再等下去也只是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,賽…賽納
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的夥伴已經早一步下黃泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你們偷賣掉一部分的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,賣掉我重要的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,貨我們會還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說﹐賽納
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的部下非常熟知\N{\fs8}\N{\r}為人體製造痛苦的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這些前東德的技術\N{\fs8}\N{\r}你們在死之前就慢慢享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你﹐等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,賽納…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,錸曼那件事怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯曼的隊伍已進入瑞士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,預計明天發動襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,即使高牆崩塌﹐過去仍無法消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,錸曼那混帳﹐你就等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是索達嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是迪塔．錸曼將軍對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是來殺我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係﹐海音茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他們的任務就是護衛我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明退役那麼多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們還是那麼關心我\N{\fs8}\N{\r}NATO也真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天下午都會去爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？願意陪我去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎﹐太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼﹐我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不﹐你們不必跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡思亂想﹐海音茲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們離遠一點保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍應該會走平常那條路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是阿爾卑斯玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,它是代表阿爾卑斯的花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妳喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然比紅色還要淡\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不過﹐比淡紅色還要充滿力道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這附近的阿爾卑斯玫瑰\N{\fs8}\N{\r}顏色特別纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的眼光很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的森林很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在退役後搬到這裡來住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我出生的德國﹐森林都很暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是以前或現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在情報部時代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我這雙手幹盡了骯髒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有時認為那麼做是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但也有相反的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不過﹐對於索達的命令\N{\fs8}\N{\r}我都忠實遵守了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道理由是什麼\N{\fs8}\N{\r}也沒去想過善惡問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:09:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以違逆索達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也因此我才能當上將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知道我要被殺的理由嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,即使這樣﹐妳也要殺我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,妳似乎很喜歡那朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,請待在這裡不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂﹐妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,人在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍﹐您有受傷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是她救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是這傢伙來襲擊我們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他以前是STG的隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧有妳的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,殺你是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這是不容遭到妨礙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我殺了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,風似乎變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看來今晚天氣會很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,白天襲擊我們的是STG
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,前東德國家保安局的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的老大康拉多．賽納
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在柏林圍牆倒塌後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,利用冷戰時代累積的經驗\N{\fs8}\N{\r}成立了一個犯罪組織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在靠走私毒品\N{\fs8}\N{\r}從中獲取莫大的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,原屬於NATO情報部的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,與賽納率領的STG\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不斷進行著激烈的對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至還利用彼此的家人互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是很愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在失去女兒之前\N{\fs8}\N{\r}完全沒察覺那麼做有多愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我女兒被賽納殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她死得真的很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,必須徹底進行復仇才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這種想法是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他們都無法脫離\N{\fs8}\N{\r}這種錯誤的連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,居然對妳這個索達使者\N{\fs8}\N{\r}說了這些沒意義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那杯紅酒味道如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不過﹐在莊園釀造的紅酒更好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莊園？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟阿爾蒂娜一起住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾蒂娜是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我雖然沒見過她\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不過﹐我聽過這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,難道妳是Noir嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,過去曾經有幾個殺手\N{\fs8}\N{\r}自稱是Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到今天\N{\fs8}\N{\r}我居然可以親眼見到Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,海音茲他們不知道索達的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,請放過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟將軍做了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要盡可能的遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎﹐錸曼死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,NATO的老狐狸終於死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這是統一之後\N{\fs8}\N{\r}最讓我開心的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,錸曼似乎是被其他人殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯曼怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,前後發生什麼事完全不明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,賓德﹐由你來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,下禮拜有新貨到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘了做確認
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,船我這邊會準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,警衛在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂﹐沒人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,喂﹐來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,還不快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,賓德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妳…妳究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看妳的臉﹐克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,妳那平安的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好多話想跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我見到那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她送了我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妳應該也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,來﹐到屋裡慢慢說給我聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:34.59,ED,,0,0,0,,輕輕地被觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:47.17,ED,,0,0,0,,終於察覺到臉頰的冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:52.94,ED,,0,0,0,,清晨醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:05.39,ED,,0,0,0,,突然開始注意到鳥鳴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:09.36,ED,,0,0,0,,什麼都還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:20.93,ED,,0,0,0,,不知內心追求的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:26.00,ED,,0,0,0,,總是望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:33.38,ED,,0,0,0,,不知何時開始這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:45.99,ED,,0,0,0,,讓思念朝著雲的下方飛去
